com.dxfeed.annotation

Enum EventFieldType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EventFieldType>
      • com.dxfeed.annotation.EventFieldType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EventFieldType>

    public enum EventFieldType
extends Enum<EventFieldType>
    Semantic type of event class field. It is used to instruct the annotation processor to use appropriate serialized form.

      • TIME_SECONDS

        public static final EventFieldType TIME_SECONDS
        This type can be used for long properties that store time in milliseconds since Java Epoch. It will be mapped to a QD field that keeps seconds since Java Epoch (milliseconds will be lost).

      • TIME_MILLIS

        public static final EventFieldType TIME_MILLIS
        This type can be used for long properties that store time in milliseconds since Java Epoch. It will be mapped to a time millis QD field.

      • DATE

        public static final EventFieldType DATE
        This type can be used for int properties that store number of days since Java Epoch.

      • INT

        public static final EventFieldType INT
        This type can be used for all primitive properties and reference types using ClassValueMapping annotaiton. It will be mapped to an integer QD field.

      • LONG

        public static final EventFieldType LONG
        This type can be used for long properties. By default primitive longs are mapped to DECIMAL - use this type with EventFieldMapping annotation to map to a long QD field.

      • DECIMAL

        public static final EventFieldType DECIMAL
        This type can be used for all primitive properties. It will be mapped to a decimal QD field.

      • CHAR

        public static final EventFieldType CHAR
        This type can be used for char properties. It will be mapped to a char QD field.

      • SHORT_STRING

        public static final EventFieldType SHORT_STRING
        This type can be used for String properties. It will be mapped to a short-string QD field that can store up to four ASCII characters.

      • STRING

        public static final EventFieldType STRING
        This type can be used for String properties. It will be mapped to a string QD field.

      • MARSHALLED

        public static final EventFieldType MARSHALLED
        This type can be used for all reference properties. It will be mapped to a serial object QD field.
